Installation

sudo apt-get update

To install pip for python 2

sudo apt-get install python-pip

for python 3

sudo apt-get install python3-pip

To find what version of pip you are running use either of the following

pip --version
pip -V

To upgrade pip itself to latest version

pip install --upgrade pip

To view the list of PyPI packages with their versions:

pip list

To install a PyPI package:

pip install <package name>

To install a specific version of a package

pip install <package name> == <package version> # specific version

To install a minimum version

pip install <package name> >= <package version> # minimal version

To list outdated packages

pip list --outdated

to show details about an installed package

pip show <package>

to search PyPI for packages

pip search <package>


Resources :

